{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a brand-new premium Shopify section from scratch that looks like it was designed by a world-class luxury eCommerce agency. This section must feel modern, high-end, visually impressive, and optimized for conversions. The design should use a dark luxury aesthetic with perfect spacing, alignment, typography hierarchy, and visual balance. Every element should feel intentional and professionally designed. The section should include a premium heading area with a small badge above the heading, a large attention-grabbing headline, and a supporting description underneath. Below this, create four premium content blocks arranged in a perfectly balanced layout.
    
    Each content block should contain a unique premium icon, a strong title, and a concise supporting description. The icons should have a premium glowing appearance and feel alive through subtle movement. The content blocks should feel interactive and luxurious rather than static. When visitors move their cursor over a block, the block should smoothly elevate, slightly increase in size, enhance its glow effect, and create a premium interactive experience. Every hover effect should feel smooth, natural, and expensive.
    
    Add advanced entrance animations throughout the entire section. When the section becomes visible on screen, the badge should appear first with a smooth fade effect. After a short delay, the headline should appear with a smooth upward motion. The description should then appear naturally, followed by each content block appearing one after another in a perfectly timed sequence. The animations should feel premium and cinematic rather than basic. Every movement should use smooth easing and professional timing.
    
    Add continuous micro-animations that run in the background without distracting users. Icons should have subtle floating movements. Background elements should have slow-moving ambient effects that create depth and sophistication. Add premium glowing accents, moving light effects, soft gradients, and subtle visual details that make the section feel alive while maintaining excellent performance.
    
    The overall structure should feel similar to what would be seen on a premium fashion, footwear, luxury, technology, or lifestyle brand website. Focus heavily on visual storytelling, luxury branding, and user engagement. The section should immediately capture attention and communicate trust, quality, innovation, and professionalism.
    
    On large screens, display all content blocks in a perfectly aligned horizontal row. On medium-sized devices, intelligently adapt the layout while maintaining visual balance. On mobile devices, transform the section into a premium swipeable experience with smooth touch interactions, snap scrolling, animated indicators, and optimized spacing. All animations and interactions must work flawlessly across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.
    
    Every visual element should be fully customizable from the Shopify Theme Editor, including headings, descriptions, icons, colors, backgrounds, spacing, button content, animation controls, content block settings, section width, and mobile behavior. The section should be designed so merchants can customize everything without modifying code.
    
    Focus obsessively on premium details including spacing consistency, typography proportions, content alignment, hover interactions, animation timing, visual hierarchy, responsiveness, conversion optimization, luxury aesthetics, and user experience. The final result should look like a custom section built for a multi-million-dollar premium brand and should feel significantly more advanced than standard Shopify sections. No generic layouts, no basic animations, and no template-like appearance. Every detail should contribute to a premium, modern, luxury user experience.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  @keyframes ai-lux-float-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
  }

  @keyframes ai-lux-glow-pulse-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes ai-lux-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes ai-lux-badge-appear-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.8);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }

  @keyframes ai-lux-gradient-shift-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  }

  .ai-lux-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    background: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    overflow: hidden;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-lux-background-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, {{ block.settings.gradient_color_1 }}, {{ block.settings.gradient_color_2 }});
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    animation: ai-lux-gradient-shift-{{ ai_gen_id }} {{ block.settings.gradient_animation_speed }}s ease infinite;
    opacity: {{ block.settings.gradient_opacity }};
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-lux-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-lux-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-lux-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.badge_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.badge_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background: {{ block.settings.badge_background }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.badge_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.badge_border_radius }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.badge_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.badge_spacing }}px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: ai-lux-badge-appear-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  .ai-lux-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    fill: {{ block.settings.badge_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-lux-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font_weight }};
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: ai-lux-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.4s;
  }

  .ai-lux-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_font_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    max-width: {{ block.settings.description_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: {{ block.settings.description_opacity }};
    opacity: 0;
    animation: ai-lux-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 1s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.6s;
  }

  .ai-lux-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.grid_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    background: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: ai-lux-fade-in-{{ ai_gen_id }} 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1s; }
  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }
  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }

  .ai-lux-card-glow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, {{ block.settings.glow_color }} 0%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-{{ block.settings.card_hover_lift }}px) scale(1.02);
    border-color: {{ block.settings.card_hover_border_color }};
    box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_y }}px {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_spread }}px {{ block.settings.card_hover_shadow_color }};
  }

  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-lux-card-glow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    opacity: {{ block.settings.glow_opacity }};
  }

  .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-lux-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .ai-lux-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    margin: 0 auto {{ block.settings.icon_spacing }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: {{ block.settings.icon_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.icon_border_radius }}px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
    animation: ai-lux-float-{{ ai_gen_id }} {{ block.settings.icon_float_speed }}s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .ai-lux-icon-glow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 120%;
    height: 120%;
    background: {{ block.settings.icon_glow_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.icon_border_radius }}px;
    filter: blur(20px);
    opacity: 0.6;
    animation: ai-lux-glow-pulse-{{ ai_gen_id }} {{ block.settings.icon_glow_speed }}s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-lux-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_title_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.card_title_font_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.card_title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.card_title_spacing }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-lux-card-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_description_font_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: {{ block.settings.card_description_color }};
    opacity: {{ block.settings.card_description_opacity }};
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-lux-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_tablet }}, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-lux-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-lux-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.7 }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal | times: 0.7 }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-lux-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.mobile_swipe_enabled %}
        display: flex;
        overflow-x: auto;
        scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
        gap: {{ block.settings.mobile_card_gap }}px;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
        scrollbar-width: none;
      {% else %}
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: {{ block.settings.mobile_card_gap }}px;
      {% endif %}
    }

    {% if block.settings.mobile_swipe_enabled %}
      .ai-lux-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
        display: none;
      }

      .ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        min-width: {{ block.settings.mobile_card_width }}%;
        scroll-snap-align: center;
      }
    {% endif %}

    .ai-lux-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-lux-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.description_font_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-lux-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.5 }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_horizontal | times: 0.5 }}px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.5 }}px;
    }

    .ai-lux-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.48 }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.48 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<luxury-features-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-lux-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-lux-background-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
  
  <div class="ai-lux-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-lux-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.badge_text != blank %}
        <div class="ai-lux-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <svg class="ai-lux-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          {{ block.settings.badge_text }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
        <h2 class="ai-lux-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.description != blank %}
        <div class="ai-lux-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.description }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="ai-lux-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% for i in (1..4) %}
        {% assign title_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_title' %}
        {% assign description_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_description' %}
        {% assign icon_key = 'card_' | append: i | append: '_icon' %}
        
        <div class="ai-lux-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-lux-card-glow-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
          
          <div class="ai-lux-icon-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <div class="ai-lux-icon-glow-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
            {% case block.settings[icon_key] %}
              {% when 'star' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% when 'diamond' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M2.7 10.3L12 21.6L21.3 10.3L18.6 2.4H5.4L2.7 10.3Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  <path d="M12 21.6V10.3M2.7 10.3H21.3M8.4 2.4L5.4 10.3L12 21.6M15.6 2.4L18.6 10.3L12 21.6" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% when 'shield' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M12 22C12 22 20 18 20 12V5L12 2L4 5V12C4 18 12 22 12 22Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% when 'lightning' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M13 2L3 14H12L11 22L21 10H12L13 2Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% when 'crown' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M2 20H22M3 8L7 12L12 4L17 12L21 8L20 20H4L3 8Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% when 'rocket' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M4.5 16.5C3 14 3 11.5 3 9C3 5.5 6 2 12 2C18 2 21 5.5 21 9C21 11.5 21 14 19.5 16.5M15 18L12 22L9 18M12 2V6M12 6C13.1046 6 14 6.89543 14 8C14 9.10457 13.1046 10 12 10C10.8954 10 10 9.10457 10 8C10 6.89543 10.8954 6 12 6Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% when 'heart' %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M20.84 4.61C20.3292 4.09901 19.7228 3.69365 19.0554 3.41708C18.3879 3.14052 17.6725 2.99817 16.95 2.99817C16.2275 2.99817 15.5121 3.14052 14.8446 3.41708C14.1772 3.69365 13.5708 4.09901 13.06 4.61L12 5.67L10.94 4.61C9.9083 3.57831 8.50903 2.99871 7.05 2.99871C5.59096 2.99871 4.19169 3.57831 3.16 4.61C2.1283 5.64169 1.54871 7.04097 1.54871 8.5C1.54871 9.95903 2.1283 11.3583 3.16 12.39L4.22 13.45L12 21.23L19.78 13.45L20.84 12.39C21.351 11.8792 21.7563 11.2728 22.0329 10.6054C22.3095 9.93789 22.4518 9.22248 22.4518 8.5C22.4518 7.77752 22.3095 7.06211 22.0329 6.39464C21.7563 5.72718 21.351 5.12075 20.84 4.61Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              {% else %}
                <svg class="ai-lux-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" stroke="{{ block.settings.icon_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
            {% endcase %}
          </div>

          {% if block.settings[title_key] != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-lux-card-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings[title_key] }}</h3>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings[description_key] != blank %}
            <p class="ai-lux-card-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings[description_key] }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</luxury-features-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class LuxuryFeatures{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.observerOptions = {
          threshold: 0.2,
          rootMargin: '0px'
        };
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.setupIntersectionObserver();
        this.setupMobileSwipe();
      }

      setupIntersectionObserver() {
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
          entries.forEach(entry => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              entry.target.style.animationPlayState = 'running';
            }
          });
        }, this.observerOptions);

        const animatedElements = this.querySelectorAll('[class*="ai-lux-"]');
        animatedElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
      }

      setupMobileSwipe() {
        const grid = this.querySelector('.ai-lux-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (!grid || window.innerWidth > 749) return;

        let isDown = false;
        let startX;
        let scrollLeft;

        grid.addEventListener('mousedown', (e) => {
          isDown = true;
          startX = e.pageX - grid.offsetLeft;
          scrollLeft = grid.scrollLeft;
        });

        grid.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
          isDown = false;
        });

        grid.addEventListener('mouseup', () => {
          isDown = false;
        });

        grid.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
          if (!isDown) return;
          e.preventDefault();
          const x = e.pageX - grid.offsetLeft;
          const walk = (x - startX) * 2;
          grid.scrollLeft = scrollLeft - walk;
        });
      }
    }

    customElements.define('luxury-features-{{ ai_gen_id }}', LuxuryFeatures{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Premium luxury features",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Badge"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "badge_text",
      "label": "Badge text",
      "default": "Premium Quality"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "badge_background",
      "label": "Background",
      "default": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "badge_border_color",
      "label": "Border color",
      "default": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2)"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "badge_text_color",
      "label": "Text color",
      "default": "#D4AF37"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "badge_font_size",
      "label": "Font size",
      "min": 10,
      "max": 16,
      "step": 1,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "badge_padding_vertical",
      "label": "Vertical padding",
      "min": 4,
      "max": 16,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 8
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "badge_padding_horizontal",
      "label": "Horizontal padding",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 32,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 16
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "badge_border_radius",
      "label": "Border radius",
      "min": 0,
      "max": 50,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 24
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "badge_spacing",
      "label": "Spacing below",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 40,
      "step": 2,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 20
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Heading"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Crafted for Excellence"
    },
